    "11950447": {
      "title": "Cubic-time parsing and learning algorithms for grammatical bigram models",
      "abstract": "This paper presents a probabilistic model of English grammar that is based upon \"grammatical bigrams\", i.e., syntactic relationships between pairs of words. Because of its simplicity, grammatical bigram models admit cubic-time parsing and unsupervised learning algorithms, which are described in detail."
